                                    <string notr="true"><![CDATA[
<h2 style="color:#FF3DA5; margin-top:0;">Welcome</h2>
<p style="color:#CFCFDB;">
PinkMart is a simple marketplace. Users can create ads, browse approved ads, add items to cart, and purchase with tokens.
</p>

<h3 style="color:#FF3DA5;">1) Create a New Ad</h3>
<ul style="color:#CFCFDB;">
  <li>Go to <b>New Ad</b> from the Main Menu.</li>
  <li>Fill in: <b>Title, Category, Price, Description</b>, and optionally choose an image.</li>
  <li>Click <b>Submit ad</b>. Your ad becomes <b>Pending</b> until the admin approves it.</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="color:#FF3DA5;">2) Shop</h3>
<ul style="color:#CFCFDB;">
  <li>Go to <b>Shop</b> to view ads that are approved by admin.</li>
  <li>Use filters (name/category/price) to find items faster.</li>
  <li>Click <b>Add to bucket</b> on an item to add it to your bucket list.</li>
  <li>You can remove items from your bucket list using the <b>Remove</b> button.</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="color:#FF3DA5;">3) Cart &amp; Purchase</h3>
<ul style="color:#CFCFDB;">
  <li>Go to <b>Cart</b> to see all items you plan to buy.</li>
  <li>Remove an item with the <b>Remove</b> button, or click <b>Remove all</b>.</li>
  <li>Enter a <b>discount code</b> (if you have one) and click <b>Apply</b>.</li>
  <li>Click <b>Purchase</b> to finalize. Items move to your <b>Profile â†’ Purchases</b>.</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="color:#FF3DA5;">4) Profile</h3>
<ul style="color:#CFCFDB;">
  <li>Update your account info (name, username, phone, email).</li>
  <li>Check wallet balance and add tokens (captcha verification may apply).</li>
  <li>See your <b>Purchases</b> and <b>My Ads</b> lists.</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="color:#FF3DA5;">Notes</h3>
<ul style="color:#CFCFDB;">
  <li>Only <b>approved ads</b> appear in Shop.</li>
  <li>Closing a page should return to Main Menu (use the <b>Back</b> button).</li>
  <li>Some actions will be validated by server later (login, purchase, discount).</li>
</ul>
